title: Grateful Dead Live at Robertson Gym, U.C.S.B. on 1977-02-27
lineage: First Set: Master Audience Cassettes (Nakamichi CR7-A) > Korg MR-2000 (DSF 1-bit/5.6 MHz) > AudioGate 24/96 > Adobe Audition CC 2024 > TLH flac2496 Second Set: Playback on Bob's Technics 1506 > Korg MR-2000 (DSF 1-bit/5.6 MHz) > AudioGate 24/96 > Adobe Audition CC 2024 > TLH flac2496
description:
Set I
New Minglewood Blues
Loser
El Paso

Peggy-O

Morning Dew

Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Keith Godchaux - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
Donna Jean Godchaux - Vocals
